item.title: Kids From the 90s Part 2
item.description: I remember back in the days, we couldn’t wait for the weekend just to go to the video game or music CD stores. Personally, every Saturday, I woke up at 8:00 am, and by 8:30 am, I was already on the bus heading downtown with my friends. The first thing I would do was visit my favorite music CD store called “Traffic” and buy a music CD. Every Saturday, I bought one CD to listen to the whole week before the next Saturday.
